ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Consenting to the Amendment to the Ta’an Kwach’an Council Self-Government Agreement
PrecisOrder consenting to the amendment of sections 1.1 and 6.2.3 of the TA’AN KWACH’AN COUNCIL SELF-GOVERNMENT AGREEMENT in order to (1) align with changes to the Ta’an Kwach’an Council’s constitution; and (2) alter the process by which the Ta’an Kwach’an Council consents to amendments of their Agreement.
